National Institute on Deafness and
Other Communication Disorders (N I D C D)

   The N I D C D conducts research on disorders of human communication,
   including on hearing, balance, smell, taste, voice, speech, and
   language.

   This is the text-only version of the web site. Go back to
   image-enhanced version.

